General Role- Worshipper(7)
There could be 3 types of prayers
1.Heavenly incantation- could respawn a person immediately
2.Earthly Incantation- could reduce respawn phases by 4 for the team members who are respawning
3.Demonic Incantation-could increase respawn phases by 2 for a enemy 
Each prayer takes 2 phases to cast except the Heavenly incantation which is immediate upon use
When dead the worshipper respawns in 6phases
This role is similar to that of a barricader(3 prayers which resets upon death)and Wizard(Respawn alteration)
